reviewText: The quality of the dvd was poor and the choice of subject matter was very disappointing.  I wouldn't recommend it.

THIS WAS THE WORST PURCHASE I EVER MADE FROM AMAZON. IT WAS SOLD AS NEW, BUT THE QUALITY WAS SO BAD I COULDN'T EVEN PLAY IT.  THE LIMITED AMOUNT I COULD SEE SEEMED VERY OUTDATED. I WAS EXTREMELY DISAPOINTED ANSD SHOCKED TO RECEIVE ANYTHING THIS POOR FROM AMAZON.
Very good movie.  Alot of information about Italy.  Helped with family members that visited Italy that year. Was just like visiting Italy myself.
